org.pathvisio.core.model

Class GroupStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pathvisio.core.model.GroupStyle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<GroupStyle>

    public class GroupStyle
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<GroupStyle>
    Extensible enum type for Group Styles. Groups can have different biological meanings (e.g. protein Complex), and can be rendered in different ways based on that.
